  "body": "#### Problem:\r\nThe scrolling is laggy in AC if a lot of data is added into AC and tried to be scrolled and swiped. Unfortunately, this cannot be reproduced on Android Emulator devices, and also not for some real devices.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Add at least 8 notifications into AC (replies, mentions, CRs)\r\n2. Open AC\r\n3. Swipe left-right for some notifs \r\n4. Try quickly scrolling to the bottom  and top\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual result:\r\n- The notifications are swiped right-left instead of scrolling down and up action\r\n- The swiping and scrolling are laggy\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/233411478-b3488362-db86-4679-9461-37041f1ad911.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected result:\r\nThe swiping and scrolling are smooth in AC\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Devices:\r\n- Huawei p20 light, Android 9\r\n\r\n#### ENV:\r\nNightly: 20 Apr 2023",
